{"id":3841,"date":"2024-02-23T10:27:55","date_gmt":"2019-12-23T04:57:55","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=3841"},"modified":"2024-02-13T19:08:25","modified_gmt":"2024-02-13T13:38:25","slug":"kitchen-island-designs-for-home","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/kitchen-island-designs-for-home\/","title":{"rendered":"Gather Your Friends Around These Classy Kitchen Island Designs"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Who doesn\u2019t dream of having a kitchen island installed in their kitchen? Somewhere you can prepare meals while the family fills you in on the day\u2019s happenings. Somewhere where the guests can join you for a drink as you assemble appetizers. Somewhere you can daydream over a hot cup of tea as the pots bubble away on the stovetop.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"2444\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/13190734\/instant-kitchen-island-makeover-ideas.jpg\" alt=\"Instantly upgrade your kitchen: explore 6 kitchen island makeover ideas\" class=\"wp-image-53927\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/13190734\/instant-kitchen-island-makeover-ideas.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/13190734\/instant-kitchen-island-makeover-ideas-115x300.jpg 115w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/13190734\/instant-kitchen-island-makeover-ideas-394x1024.jpg 394w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/13190734\/instant-kitchen-island-makeover-ideas-768x1997.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/13190734\/instant-kitchen-island-makeover-ideas-50x130.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/13190734\/instant-kitchen-island-makeover-ideas-591x1536.jpg 591w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/13190734\/instant-kitchen-island-makeover-ideas-788x2048.jpg 788w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/13190734\/instant-kitchen-island-makeover-ideas-150x390.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>A kitchen island, depending on how you design it, can be all this and more. They can be handsome and stunning additions ratcheting up the style quotient of the space. Read our series on 20 stunning kitchen islands to find one that fits right into your home.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Seated Affair With This Kitchen Island Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This striking black kitchen island is enhanced with additional seating. The design is kept simple and sleek with a white countertop contrasting white. Further, in keeping with the proportions of the kitchen, it is a small kitchen island allowing for plenty of movement around. The black and white bar stools add glamour, and face outside making for a great view of coconut palms over your morning cup of tea.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"820\" height=\"820\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234640\/kitchen-island-with-seated-bar-stools.jpg\" alt=\"Kitchen island design with bar stools boost the elegance of the simple but stylish black kitchen island\" class=\"wp-image-3850\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234640\/kitchen-island-with-seated-bar-stools.jpg 820w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234640\/kitchen-island-with-seated-bar-stools-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234640\/kitchen-island-with-seated-bar-stools-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234640\/kitchen-island-with-seated-bar-stools-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234640\/kitchen-island-with-seated-bar-stools-415x415.jpg 415w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234640\/kitchen-island-with-seated-bar-stools-417x416.jpg 417w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234640\/kitchen-island-with-seated-bar-stools-225x225.jpg 225w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234640\/kitchen-island-with-seated-bar-stools-475x475.jpg 475w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234640\/kitchen-island-with-seated-bar-stools-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Bar stools boost the elegance of the simple but stylish black kitchen island<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Want modular kitchen interior design with islands for extra storage\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180940\/want-modular-kitchen-interior-design-with-islands-for-extra-storage.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The Elegance Of White<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The spacious and luxurious white kitchen has a lovely kitchen island, with dimensions proportional to the rest of the kitchen. The kitchen island has shaker style cabinets and is topped with white marble adding to the pristine and elegant look of the kitchen. The U-shaped kitchen with an island is finished with accessories such as pendants over the island and appliances such as the double door furniture done up in stainless steel.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"820\" height=\"820\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234655\/white-kitchen-island-interior-design.jpg\" alt=\"White kitchen island fits right into a white kitchen with stainless steel accents\" class=\"wp-image-3853\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234655\/white-kitchen-island-interior-design.jpg 820w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234655\/white-kitchen-island-interior-design-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234655\/white-kitchen-island-interior-design-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234655\/white-kitchen-island-interior-design-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234655\/white-kitchen-island-interior-design-415x415.jpg 415w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234655\/white-kitchen-island-interior-design-417x416.jpg 417w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234655\/white-kitchen-island-interior-design-225x225.jpg 225w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234655\/white-kitchen-island-interior-design-475x475.jpg 475w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234655\/white-kitchen-island-interior-design-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">An all-white kitchen island fits right into a white kitchen with stainless steel accents<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The More Levels The Merrier<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A multi-level kitchen island design affords many benefits. The lower level is at the kitchen counter height and serves as preparation space. The higher level becomes the bar counter and adds interesting visual detail. The design works well in a small kitchen in which you need a kitchen island with seating and counter space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"820\" height=\"820\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234704\/multi-level-kitchen-island-interior-design.jpg\" alt=\"Multi-level kitchen island interior designs with kitchen counter and bar counter for small kitchen\" class=\"wp-image-3855\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234704\/multi-level-kitchen-island-interior-design.jpg 820w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234704\/multi-level-kitchen-island-interior-design-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234704\/multi-level-kitchen-island-interior-design-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234704\/multi-level-kitchen-island-interior-design-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234704\/multi-level-kitchen-island-interior-design-415x415.jpg 415w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234704\/multi-level-kitchen-island-interior-design-417x416.jpg 417w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234704\/multi-level-kitchen-island-interior-design-225x225.jpg 225w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234704\/multi-level-kitchen-island-interior-design-475x475.jpg 475w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234704\/multi-level-kitchen-island-interior-design-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Levels of varying heights bring functional and architectural advantages<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">It Doesn\u2019t Always Have To Match<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Many kitchen island styles that you see will be such that the kitchen island exactly matches the cabinets, down to the finish and colour. Proving that the trend can be successfully bucked is this white kitchen island in a vintage green kitchen. The countertops and backsplash material are the same resulting in a cohesive look. Sleek black and metal of the chairs and hanging pendant light further complete the look.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"820\" height=\"820\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234708\/kitchen-island-matches-cabinets-finish-colour.jpg\" alt=\"Kitchen island exactly matches the cabinets, down to the finish and colour\" class=\"wp-image-3856\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234708\/kitchen-island-matches-cabinets-finish-colour.jpg 820w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234708\/kitchen-island-matches-cabinets-finish-colour-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234708\/kitchen-island-matches-cabinets-finish-colour-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234708\/kitchen-island-matches-cabinets-finish-colour-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234708\/kitchen-island-matches-cabinets-finish-colour-415x415.jpg 415w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234708\/kitchen-island-matches-cabinets-finish-colour-417x416.jpg 417w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234708\/kitchen-island-matches-cabinets-finish-colour-225x225.jpg 225w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234708\/kitchen-island-matches-cabinets-finish-colour-475x475.jpg 475w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234708\/kitchen-island-matches-cabinets-finish-colour-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Make your own statement by going against the \u2018it must match\u2019 trend<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Multi-Taskers For Small Kitchens<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Owners of small kitchens rest your mind \u2013 and your dishes and utensils down. As this kitchen island example shows, a well-designed island can do wonders for your space. Organizers and drawers are fitted into the island to provide extra cabinet storage. The countertop has an induction stove fitted in, making cooking a breeze. There is a counter space left over for you to rest your prepped ingredients while you cook. Finally, all you need is to add some bar stools to make a breakfast bar at the raised level.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"820\" height=\"820\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234718\/kitchen-island-multi-taskers-for-small-kitchens.jpg\" alt=\"Well-designed kitchen island for your space with organizers and drawers are fitted into the island to provide extra cabinet storage\" class=\"wp-image-3858\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234718\/kitchen-island-multi-taskers-for-small-kitchens.jpg 820w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234718\/kitchen-island-multi-taskers-for-small-kitchens-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234718\/kitchen-island-multi-taskers-for-small-kitchens-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234718\/kitchen-island-multi-taskers-for-small-kitchens-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234718\/kitchen-island-multi-taskers-for-small-kitchens-415x415.jpg 415w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234718\/kitchen-island-multi-taskers-for-small-kitchens-417x416.jpg 417w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234718\/kitchen-island-multi-taskers-for-small-kitchens-225x225.jpg 225w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234718\/kitchen-island-multi-taskers-for-small-kitchens-475x475.jpg 475w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234718\/kitchen-island-multi-taskers-for-small-kitchens-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Small kitchens benefit tremendously by the addition of a multi-purpose island<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Do you know which modular kitchen is durable & safe\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/02170613\/which-modular-kitchen-is-durable-and-safe.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Going Sleek With Sliding Doors<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This L shaped kitchen with island has something unique about it \u2013 none of the cabinet doors or drawers have handles or knobs. Instead mechanisms like push latches give the kitchen a minimalist and sleek look. The lines of the kitchen island with seating imitates the overall look. The storage space in it has sliding doors with built-in recessed handles ensuring a smooth and flat look.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"820\" height=\"820\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234723\/l-shaped-kitchen-island-with-sliding-doors.jpg\" alt=\"L shaped kitchen with island give the kitchen a sleek look and these kitchen islands with sliding doors and recessed handles\" class=\"wp-image-3859\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234723\/l-shaped-kitchen-island-with-sliding-doors.jpg 820w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234723\/l-shaped-kitchen-island-with-sliding-doors-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234723\/l-shaped-kitchen-island-with-sliding-doors-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234723\/l-shaped-kitchen-island-with-sliding-doors-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234723\/l-shaped-kitchen-island-with-sliding-doors-415x415.jpg 415w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234723\/l-shaped-kitchen-island-with-sliding-doors-417x416.jpg 417w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234723\/l-shaped-kitchen-island-with-sliding-doors-225x225.jpg 225w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234723\/l-shaped-kitchen-island-with-sliding-doors-475x475.jpg 475w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234723\/l-shaped-kitchen-island-with-sliding-doors-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Store The Bar Stools Away<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Don\u2019t want to waste precious kitchen floor space on bar stools, yet want a few to go with your kitchen island? Or you simply don\u2019t like the look the stools cluttering up the same. Our next kitchen island with seating is tailor made for you.&nbsp; Storage space has been kept to a minimum in this modern island kitchen. Some island space has been given over to a sink and its plumbing. The rest of it is kept empty forms a home for the bar stools when they are not in use.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"820\" height=\"820\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234733\/modern-island-kitchen-with-store-bar-stools.jpg\" alt=\"Modern island kitchen interiors by simply pull the bar stools out and settle in for a cosy conversation\" class=\"wp-image-3861\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234733\/modern-island-kitchen-with-store-bar-stools.jpg 820w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234733\/modern-island-kitchen-with-store-bar-stools-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234733\/modern-island-kitchen-with-store-bar-stools-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.