m\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234737\/kitchen-island-design-sweet-deal-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234737\/kitchen-island-design-sweet-deal-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234737\/kitchen-island-design-sweet-deal-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234737\/kitchen-island-design-sweet-deal-415x415.jpg 415w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234737\/kitchen-island-design-sweet-deal-417x416.jpg 417w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234737\/kitchen-island-design-sweet-deal-225x225.jpg 225w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234737\/kitchen-island-design-sweet-deal-475x475.jpg 475w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234737\/kitchen-island-design-sweet-deal-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">The in-built oven brings additional functionality to this breath-taking kitchen island<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">No More Sinking Feelings<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The U-shaped kitchen with island gives us all the feels. The kitchen is done up all in white with stainless steel appliances. The island, with its white cabinetry, is in line with the space\u2019s aesthetic style. It has the added benefit of having a sink installed in it. The metal finish of the sink fittings and the very handily positioned rail are practical and augment the sleek finish of the kitchen.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"820\" height=\"820\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234742\/kitchen-island-with-sink.jpg\" alt=\"U shaped kitchen with island gives a sink into your kitchen island for a convenient source of water supply\" class=\"wp-image-3863\" srcset=\"