igure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"820\" height=\"820\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234747\/kitchen-island-table-breakfast-bar-as-workstation-1.jpg\" alt=\"Kitchen island table is perfect for those wanting to utilise breakfast bar as workstation\" class=\"wp-image-3864\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234747\/kitchen-island-table-breakfast-bar-as-workstation-1.jpg 820w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234747\/kitchen-island-table-breakfast-bar-as-workstation-1-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234747\/kitchen-island-table-breakfast-bar-as-workstation-1-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234747\/kitchen-island-table-breakfast-bar-as-workstation-1-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234747\/kitchen-island-table-breakfast-bar-as-workstation-1-415x415.jpg 415w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234747\/kitchen-island-table-breakfast-bar-as-workstation-1-417x416.jpg 417w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234747\/kitchen-island-table-breakfast-bar-as-workstation-1-225x225.jpg 225w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234747\/kitchen-island-table-breakfast-bar-as-workstation-1-475x475.jpg 475w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234747\/kitchen-island-table-breakfast-bar-as-workstation-1-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">From leisurely breakfasts to an opportune workspace, this kitchen island hosts it all<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Light and Airy<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This black kitchen island is far from being a black hole that sucks all sense of spaciousness from the room. In fact, it does quite the opposite. The trick lies in having open storage. The shelves provide extra storage but as they are open, they make the kitchen look spacious and fresh.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"820\" height=\"820\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234751\/storage-in-kitchen-island-open.jpg\" alt=\"Keeping the storage in the kitchen island open and shelves provide extra storage but as they are open\" class=\"wp-image-3865\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234751\/storage-in-kitchen-island-open.jpg 820w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234751\/storage-in-kitchen-island-open-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234751\/storage-in-kitchen-island-open-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234751\/storage-in-kitchen-island-open-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234751\/storage-in-kitchen-island-open-415x415.jpg 415w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234751\/storage-in-kitchen-island-open-417x416.jpg 417w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234751\/storage-in-kitchen-island-open-225x225.jpg 225w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234751\/storage-in-kitchen-island-open-475x475.jpg 475w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234751\/storage-in-kitchen-island-open-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Achieve an airy and spacious look by keeping the storage in the kitchen island open<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Divide and Conquer<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The small kitchen island featured here does a splendid job of separating the kitchen from the dining space. The narrow dimensions of the kitchen mean that installing the kitchen island in the middle blocks the flow of movement. Positioning it at the imaginary threshold of the kitchen allows it to act like a divider, a buffet board and an extra counter.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"820\" height=\"820\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234759\/separating-kitchen-island-from-dining-space.jpg\" alt=\"Small kitchen island featured separating the kitchen from the dining space\" class=\"wp-image-3867\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234759\/separating-kitchen-island-from-dining-space.jpg 820w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234759\/separating-kitchen-island-from-dining-space-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234759\/separating-kitchen-island-from-dining-space-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234759\/separating-kitchen-island-from-dining-space-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234759\/separating-kitchen-island-from-dining-space-415x415.jpg 415w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234759\/separating-kitchen-island-from-dining-space-417x416.jpg 417w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234759\/separating-kitchen-island-from-dining-space-225x225.jpg 225w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234759\/separating-kitchen-island-from-dining-space-475x475.jpg 475w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234759\/separating-kitchen-island-from-dining-space-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Position the kitchen island such that it zones an open kitchen area<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Lean It In<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Continuing the trend of unconventional placement is this kitchen island example. Instead of being centered in the kitchen, it\u2019s narrow end it placed against a wall. The positioning is done so that it seems to be at the base of the eye-catching tree design that adorns the wall. There is plenty of storage, both shut and open. Trendy bar stools make for some cool seating. Contemporary light pendants round the look off nicely.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"820\" height=\"820\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234808\/positioning-kitchen-island-against-wall.jpg\" alt=\"Space for movement by positioning the kitchen island against the wall\" class=\"wp-image-3869\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234808\/positioning-kitchen-island-against-wall.jpg 820w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234808\/positioning-kitchen-island-against-wall-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234808\/positioning-kitchen-island-against-wall-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234808\/positioning-kitchen-island-against-wall-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234808\/positioning-kitchen-island-against-wall-415x415.jpg 415w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234808\/positioning-kitchen-island-against-wall-417x416.jpg 417w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234808\/positioning-kitchen-island-against-wall-225x225.jpg 225w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234808\/positioning-kitchen-island-against-wall-475x475.jpg 475w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234808\/positioning-kitchen-island-against-wall-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Kitchen Island Design That Makes Freezing A Breeze<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are someone whose refrigerator\u2019s freezer section is full to the brim, you will appreciate the practical use that this kitchen island design provides. It has an inbuilt freezer drawer, storage cupboards and drawers and a useful sink. Together, they make for very easy meal preparation in this open plan space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"820\" height=\"820\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234813\/kitchen-island-design-with-freezer-drawer-storage-cupboards-sink.jpg\" alt=\"Kitchen island designs complete with freezer drawer, storage cupboards and drawers and a useful sink\" class=\"wp-image-3870\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234813\/kitchen-island-design-with-freezer-drawer-storage-cupboards-sink.jpg 820w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234813\/kitchen-island-design-with-freezer-drawer-storage-cupboards-sink-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234813\/kitchen-island-design-with-freezer-drawer-storage-cupboards-sink-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234813\/kitchen-island-design-with-freezer-drawer-storage-cupboards-sink-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234813\/kitchen-island-design-with-freezer-drawer-storage-cupboards-sink-415x415.jpg 415w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234813\/kitchen-island-design-with-freezer-drawer-storage-cupboards-sink-417x416.jpg 417w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234813\/kitchen-island-design-with-freezer-drawer-storage-cupboards-sink-225x225.jpg 225w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234813\/kitchen-island-design-with-freezer-drawer-storage-cupboards-sink-475x475.jpg 475w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234813\/kitchen-island-design-with-freezer-drawer-storage-cupboards-sink-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Meal prep is far from a chore with this kitchen island complete with storage and a freezer drawer<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Super-Size The Kitchen Island<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>In a world where everything from pizzas to beverages can be super-sized, why should the kitchen island be left behind? This white kitchen with island has plenty of space and it is showing it off in style. The U-shaped kitchen has a large island placed at it center in line with the cabinetry. While the cabinetry in the rest of the kitchen is white, the island retains the natural notes of wood doing justice to the hardwood floors.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"820\" height=\"820\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234823\/u-shaped-island-kitchen-interior-design.jpg\" alt=\"U shaped kitchen interior design has a large island placed at it center in line with the cabinetry\" class=\"wp-image-3872\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234823\/u-shaped-island-kitchen-interior-design.jpg 820w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234823\/u-shaped-island-kitchen-interior-design-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234823\/u-shaped-island-kitchen-interior-design-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234823\/u-shaped-island-kitchen-interior-design-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234823\/u-shaped-island-kitchen-interior-design-415x415.jpg 415w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234823\/u-shaped-island-kitchen-interior-design-417x416.jpg 417w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234823\/u-shaped-island-kitchen-interior-design-225x225.jpg 225w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234823\/u-shaped-island-kitchen-interior-design-475x475.jpg 475w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234823\/u-shaped-island-kitchen-interior-design-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A large kitchen island brings warmth and coziness to this spacious kitchen<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Keep It Cool<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>After all those U-shaped kitchens, let\u2019s turn to an L-shaped kitchen with an island. This one is situated in an open floor plan modern loft and is done up in stylish black and white. The kitchen island doubles up as a table, a stove top and a countertop. It\u2019s mix of colours and finishes echo the modern style of d\u00e9cor of the studio.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"820\" height=\"820\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234836\/modern-l-shaped-kitchen-with-island.jpg\" alt=\"L shaped kitchen with island is the trendy kitchen island plays it cool in keeping with modern space\" class=\"wp-image-3875\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234836\/modern-l-shaped-kitchen-with-island.jpg 820w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234836\/modern-l-shaped-kitchen-with-island-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234836\/modern-l-shaped-kitchen-with-island-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234836\/modern-l-shaped-kitchen-with-island-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234836\/modern-l-shaped-kitchen-with-island-415x415.jpg 415w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234836\/modern-l-shaped-kitchen-with-island-417x416.jpg 417w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234836\/modern-l-shaped-kitchen-with-island-225x225.jpg 225w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234836\/modern-l-shaped-kitchen-with-island-475x475.jpg 475w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234836\/modern-l-shaped-kitchen-with-island-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">The trendy kitchen island plays it cool in keeping with the modern space<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Cool kitchen design hacks on a budget\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/17140431\/cool-kitchen-design-hacks-on-budget.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Carving Curves Out Of Granite<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Moving on from the very modern to the classical. This L-shaped kitchen island is luxuriously appointed with cherrywood cabinets and stone countertops. What makes the kitchen island with granite countertop unique is the shape of the granite slab. While the end that is used as counter space is kept plain, the breakfast bar side is graciously curved. Period chandeliers drop from the ceiling above the island. The overall effect while being richly gorgeous is also cosy and welcoming.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"820\" height=\"820\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234847\/classical-l-shaped-kitchen-with-island.jpg\" alt=\"Classical l shaped kitchen interior design with island with the curved lines of the granite topped kitchen island\" class=\"wp-image-3877\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234847\/classical-l-shaped-kitchen-with-island.jpg 820w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234847\/classical-l-shaped-kitchen-with-island-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234847\/classical-l-shaped-kitchen-with-island-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234847\/classical-l-shaped-kitchen-with-island-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234847\/classical-l-shaped-kitchen-with-island-415x415.jpg 415w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234847\/classical-l-shaped-kitchen-with-island-417x416.jpg 417w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234847\/classical-l-shaped-kitchen-with-island-225x225.jpg 225w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234847\/classical-l-shaped-kitchen-with-island-475x475.jpg 475w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234847\/classical-l-shaped-kitchen-with-island-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">The curved lines of the granite topped kitchen island invite you to linger over your morning coffee<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Wheeling The Colours In<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Adding wonderful teals and blues to otherwise plain white kitchen is this whimsically designed kitchen island on wheels. The island is finished retro style with the MDF doors painted such that the blues merging with the greens. It is mounted on castors making it moveable. When choosing such a kitchen island design make sure the castors of top quality and strong enough to bear the weight of the island.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"820\" height=\"820\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234852\/kitchen-island-design-colours.jpg\" alt=\"Kitchen island is finished retro style with the mdf doors painted such that the blues merging with the greens\" class=\"wp-image-3878\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234852\/kitchen-island-design-colours.jpg 820w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234852\/kitchen-island-design-colours-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234852\/kitchen-island-design-colours-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234852\/kitchen-island-design-colours-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234852\/kitchen-island-design-colours-415x415.jpg 415w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234852\/kitchen-island-design-colours-417x416.jpg 417w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234852\/kitchen-island-design-colours-225x225.jpg 225w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234852\/kitchen-island-design-colours-475x475.jpg 475w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234852\/kitchen-island-design-colours-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">The easy to move kitchen island scores very high on the style and utility scales<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">For Carting Around<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Continuing our series of moveable kitchen islands is this kitchen island cart. It may be a small kitchen island but it sure packs a punch. It has both standard legs and wheels making it stable and yet easy to wheel when required. The size of the cart makes it ideal to be stationed in the kitchen and to be transported.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"820\" height=\"820\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234856\/moveable-kitchen-islands.jpg\" alt=\"this small kitchen island has a movable cart makes it ideal to be stationed in the kitchen and to be transported.\" class=\"wp-image-3880\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234856\/moveable-kitchen-islands.jpg 820w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234856\/moveable-kitchen-islands-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234856\/moveable-kitchen-islands-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234856\/moveable-kitchen-islands-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234856\/moveable-kitchen-islands-415x415.jpg 415w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234856\/moveable-kitchen-islands-417x416.jpg 417w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234856\/moveable-kitchen-islands-225x225.jpg 225w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234856\/moveable-kitchen-islands-475x475.jpg 475w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20234856\/moveable-kitchen-islands-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">We are in love with the cuteness of the kitchen island cart!<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Slot It With Slats<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We end our series on stunning kitchen islands with yet another black kitchen island. But this time it is a kitchen island on wheels. The fabulous powder blue kitchen needed some black to make it go from good to great. The kitchen island does exactly that. Its black stylish finish works as a counterpoint to the rest of the kitchen while its stainless-steel countertop mirrors the appliances and the hood over the stove. Wheels make it double up as a convenient kitchen island cart.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"820\" height=\"820\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235026\/slatted-shelves-design-kitchen-island-cart-1.jpg\" alt=\"Kitchen island on wheels these wheels make it double up as a convenient kitchen island cart\" class=\"wp-image-3912\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235026\/slatted-shelves-design-kitchen-island-cart-1.jpg 820w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235026\/slatted-shelves-design-kitchen-island-cart-1-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235026\/slatted-shelves-design-kitchen-island-cart-1-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235026\/slatted-shelves-design-kitchen-island-cart-1-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235026\/slatted-shelves-design-kitchen-island-cart-1-415x415.jpg 415w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235026\/slatted-shelves-design-kitchen-island-cart-1-417x416.jpg 417w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235026\/slatted-shelves-design-kitchen-island-cart-1-225x225.jpg 225w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235026\/slatted-shelves-design-kitchen-island-cart-1-475x475.jpg 475w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235026\/slatted-shelves-design-kitchen-island-cart-1-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">The slatted shelves design and black and metal exterior make the moveable kitchen island ideal for the kitchen<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope these island kitchen designs have left you longing to redo your space. Your mealtime is going to get a whole lot more wholesome and enjoyable as you gather your friends and family around.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Check out:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/guides\/different-types-of-kitchen-layouts\/\">A Guide To Different Types of Kitchen Layouts<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Modular Kitchens At Best Prices<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Speak to our kitchen experts today!<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n        <!-- <div class=\"form-group col-md-3 guideForm\">\n            <select name=\"your-phone-ext\" id=\"id_select2_example\" class=\"id_select2_example drop-downfield form-dropdown\"\n                onfocus='this.size=5;' onblur='this.size=1;' onchange='this.size=1; this.blur();'\n                data-width=\"100%\" data-minimum-results-for-search=\"Infinity\">\n               \n                <option value=\"+01\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06163948\/01.png\">\n                    +01\n                <\/option>\n                <option value=\"+91\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06164015\/91.png\"\n                    selected>\n                    +91\n                <\/option>\n                <option value=\"+44\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/me